[SN]TITLE[SN]
Ship remains revealed using special underwater drone

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Scientists in America are working with a new type of drone - but instead of flying high up into the sky, this one goes deep underwater.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
20 July 2016 Last updated at 17:05 BST
The special drone can search for objects 100m under the surface of the water.
It's been exploring an old steam ship at the bottom of a lake in Nevada, America.
Ricky has been finding out more...
